    <briefdescription>
<para>Abstract interface for knob value constraints. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classhipdnn__frontend_1_1IConstraint" kindref="compound">IConstraint</ref> defines the interface for validating knob settings. Different constraint types (integer, float, string) implement this interface.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="classhipdnn__frontend_1_1IntConstraint" kindref="compound">IntConstraint</ref>, <ref refid="classhipdnn__frontend_1_1FloatConstraint" kindref="compound">FloatConstraint</ref>, <ref refid="classhipdnn__frontend_1_1StringConstraint" kindref="compound">StringConstraint</ref> </para>
